@startuml
title Viaverse Observability / Trace / Log / Metric — Sequence Diagram

actor Client
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Domain Service" as Service
participant "OpenTelemetry SDK/Collector" as Otel
database "Prometheus" as Prometheus
database "Jaeger" as Jaeger
database "OpenSearch Logs" as Logs
participant "Alerting / Ops" as Alert

Client -> Gateway : request + traceparent
Gateway -> Service : forward with correlationId
Service -> Otel : create span + attributes
Service -> Otel : record metric/log context
Otel -> Prometheus : export metrics
Otel -> Jaeger : export traces
Otel -> Logs : export structured logs
Prometheus -> Alert : SLO/error threshold
Logs -> Alert : error pattern/anomaly
Jaeger -> Alert : latency regression

note bottom
CorrelationId and traceparent travel from gateway to every service.
Logs, traces and metrics must be joinable without exposing secrets.
end note
@enduml
